FORRESTER v. WARDEN OF THE MARYLAND PENITENTIARY [App. No. 87,

September Term, 1964.]

Decided August 5, 1965.

Before Prescott, C. J., and Hammond, Horney, Marbury, Sybert, OppEnheimer and Barnes, JJ.

Per Curiam.

For the reasons assigned by Judge Foster below the application must be denied.

Application denied.
